title: Anarchist Cookbook - William Powell [the.wheel].pdf
description:
The Anarchist Cookbook by William Powell

Perhaps the most notorious How To manual on the market. This is the most asked for book that we know of. Is it any good? Well, it's now in its 29th printing since 1971, has chapters on home preparation of weapons, electronics, drugs, and explosives.
